{"tid":2310471,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"foodpanda請試食員 月薪高達3.5萬連伙食費","createTime":"2020-12-03T09:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T07:03:06.000Z","uid":66271,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5f9fb24e715978c01af7cc92c31b8d52ab9aa3a2","tid":2310471,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:37:59.000Z","msg":"你是一名「吃貨」嗎？如果你自問「好擦得」，喜歡周圍發掘新餐廳，而且懂得拍出引人流口水的美食照，那麼這份超級筍工簡直是為你而設。外賣平台foodpanda近日宣布招聘「首席試食員」（Chief Makan Officer），試食員每月可獲得6,000新加坡元（約3.5萬港元）伙食費兼薪金，十分吸引。<br />\n<br />\n根據foodpanda的網站資料顯示，首席試食員的工作相當簡單，只需要到訪與foodpanda合作的餐廳進行試食，並就到訪的經驗撰寫一篇吸引人的文章。試食員除了有機會嘗到多達1.5萬間合作餐廳的美食外，也可優先瀏覽和購買foodpanda旗下網店pandamart的產品。靠著一把口，每月即可獲得1,000新加坡元（約5,788港元）基本月薪，以及額外5,000新加坡元（約2.9萬港元）伙食費，合共約3.5萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foodpanda.sg/zh/contents/chief-makan-officer?r=1https://paper.hket.com/article/2817596/%E6%98%9Ffoodpanda%E8%81%98%E8%A9%A6%E9%A3%9F%E5%93%A1%20%E4%BC%99%E9%A3%9F%E8%B2%BB%E5%85%BC%E6%9C%88%E8%96%AA%E9%81%943.5%E8%90%AC?mtc=70030\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foodpanda.sg%2Fzh%2Fcontents%2Fchief-makan-officer%3Fr%3D1https%3A%2F%2Fpaper.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2817596%2F%25E6%2598%259Ffoodpanda%25E8%2581%2598%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%2593%25A1%2520%25E4%25BC%2599%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E5%2585%25BC%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%2596%25AA%25E9%2581%25943.5%25E8%2590%25AC%3Fmtc%3D70030&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPe2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=6e19a0d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.foodpanda.sg/zh/contents/chief-makan-officer?r=1https://paper.hket.com/article/2817596/%E6%98%9Ffoodpanda%E8%81%98%E8%A9%A6%E9%A3%9F%E5%93%A1%20%E4%BC%99%E9%A3%9F%E8%B2%BB%E5%85%BC%E6%9C%88%E8%96%AA%E9%81%943.5%E8%90%AC?mtc=70030</a>"},{"pid":"321375f9871e8ec8902e272d1f083cd6168b70f2","tid":2310471,"uid":186727,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:44:48.000Z","msg":"正。要去見工了"},{"pid":"ccb0ed7fedf7d0bd339a98af7961699f1da56401","tid":2310471,"uid":356930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T10:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a0bbb33dfef9388512e9fa9779e3b4dd0f31ce","tid":2310471,"uid":27664,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T10:32:08.000Z","msg":"只需要到訪與foodpanda合作的餐廳進行試食，並就到訪的經驗<strong><span class=\"red\">撰寫一篇吸引人的文章</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">想行以前Openrice條路</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f37ce561092754a30e7e239fbbd049256ac2dd","tid":2310471,"uid":59511,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T10:33:37.000Z","msg":"係5千幾蚊月薪+差唔多3萬嘅伙食費，即係話平時去食嘢冇得再claim錢，想食平少少慳錢都唔得，因為食邊間唔係自己揀"},{"pid":"22948051ee3e0d37c09399295454fab64986a565","tid":2310471,"uid":363330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T10:34:41.000Z","msg":".sg<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f80313de1e1e3a5213e49ba137a687c7546e2d4","tid":2310471,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T06:53:37.000Z","msg":"係咪即係1000坡紙請放蛇員?<br />\n向屋企俾你叫5000坡紙<br />\n但其實成本可能唔洗2000"},{"pid":"4451bb03b6656f0df72a960c8c99d745e3b3d8ea","tid":2310471,"uid":320293,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T06:59:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ee6c2178acfe8d508d8898b3ec6771668b6fc39","tid":2310471,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4451bb03b6656f0df72a960c8c99d745e3b3d8ea","tid":2310471,"uid":320293,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T06:59:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T07:03:06.000Z","msg":"但係條link through Singapore"}]}